com.github.rolecraftdev.util

Class ProfessionDeserializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.rolecraftdev.util.ProfessionDeserializer

  • public class ProfessionDeserializer
extends Object
    A class which can be used to extract a Profession and all its related classes (except for ProfessionManager) from a YAML file by using appropriate deserialization.
